"Grylli includes built-in instructions throughout the app to help you "
"configure and manage your setup."
msgstr ""
"Grylli sizga sozlamalarni tuzish va boshqarishda yordam berish uchun dastur "
"bo'ylab o'rnatilgan ko'rsatmalarni o'z ichiga oladi."

#: app/templates/help.html:8
msgid ""
"This page provides an overview of key features and direct links to where "
"they can be managed."
msgstr ""
"Ushbu sahifa asosiy funksiyalar ko'rinishini taqdim etadi va ularni qayerda "
"boshqarilishi mumkin bo'lgan to'g'ridan-to'g'ri havolalar mavjud."

